				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2076208/decisions-we-make#post-4845075</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 15 Dec 2020 03:14:13 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>DarkStuff</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1581620</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Very sweet, and I like that Sasha's relationship to her family has been developed a bit. For the record, I like that last name Merlo better than Grimmer, but something told me (to use an outdated and perhaps slightly insensitive saying) Sasha &quot;wore the pants&quot; in the relationship to the point that I was almost sure Gabe took <em>her</em> name. Tradition dies hard, I guess, heheh. It's just funny. I didn't realize I had that assumption until it was proven the other way around and I was legitimately surprised.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
